    dc:description "Figure 1. Adults of Phaecadophora spp. A P. dactylina sp. nov. (holotype, male) B P. dactylina sp. nov. (paratype, female) C P. vascularis sp. nov. (holotype, male). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
